Usage: selectNet [-help] { <netName> | -allDefClock  | -clock  | -nonDefaultRule  | -shield  }

-help            # Prints out the command usage
<net>*           # Specify the net name ((net)*, optional)
-allDefClock     # Selects all nets that have a DEF attribute + USE CLOCK
                 # (bool, optional)
-clock           # Select all clock nets (bool, optional)
-nonDefaultRule  # Select all nets that have a DEF attribute + USE
                 # NONDEFAULTRULE (bool, optional)
-shield          # Select all nets that have a DEF attribute + USE SHIELDNETS
                 # (bool, optional)